This is to inform all fresh students, their sponsors/parents, well wishers as well as members of the general public that the 36th Matriculation Ceremony of the Abia State University, Uturu has been scheduled for the 2017/2018 academic session.  The matriculation ceremony will hold on Thursday 1st March, 2018. ABSU 36TH MATRICULATION CEREMONY 2017/18 The Vice … The post Abia State University 2017/2018 Matriculation Ceremony Date Announced. appeared first on Students Nigeria. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from Students Nigeria. Click here to read the full text on the original website.